        Association of Mathematical Sciences
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
        Talks, problem solving, and student research at Stevens.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-600">
        © {year} AMS · Stevens Institute of Technology
